# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok russian prosecutors presented new charges monday against former oil tycoon mikhail khodorkovsky , who is already serving a jail sentence for fraud and tax evasion , khodorkovsky 's lawyer said , interfax reported .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (o / organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Interpol"))
      :ARG1 (p / present-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (p3 / prosecute-01)
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Russia")))
            :ARG1 (c2 / charge-05
                  :ARG1 (p4 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Mikhail"
                              :op2 "Khodorkovsky")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG2 (t / tycoon
                                    :mod (o2 / oil))
                              :time (f / former))
                        :ARG0-of (s / serve-04
                              :ARG1 (s2 / sentence-01
                                    :ARG1 p4
                                    :ARG2 (a / and
                                          :op1 (d / defraud-01
                                                :ARG0 p4)
                                          :op2 (e / evade-01
                                                :ARG0 p4
                                                :ARG1 (t2 / tax-01)))
                                    :location (j / jail))
                              :time (a2 / already)))
                  :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok dhirubhai ambani , the founder and chairman of india 's largest private sector company reliance industries who began his working life as a gas station attendant , has died .
# ::alignments
(d / die-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "dhirubhai"
                  :op2 "Ambani")
            :ARG0-of (f / found-01
                  :ARG1 (c / company
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 " reliance"
                              :op2 "Industries")
                        :mod (s / sector
                              :ARG1-of (p2 / private-03))
                        :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (l / large)
                              :ARG3 (m / most)
                              :ARG5 (c2 / company
                                    :location (c3 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "India"))))))
            :ARG0-of (b / begin-01
                  :ARG1 (l2 / life
                        :mod (w / work-01
                              :ARG0 p))
                  :manner (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (a / attend-02
                              :ARG1 (s2 / station
                                    :location-of (g / gas-03)))))
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (c4 / chairman))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok tens of thousands of volunteers from across the united states poured into mississippi and louisiana and performed heroic service after hurricane katrina .
# ::alignments

      :op1 (p / pour-01
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (v / volunteer-01)
                  :quant (m / multiple
                        :op1 10000)
                  :source (a2 / across
                        :op1 (s / state
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States"))))
            :ARG3 (a3 / and
                  :op1 (s2 / state
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Mississippi"))
                  :op2 (s3 / state
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Louisiana"))))
      :op2 (p3 / perform-02
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (s4 / serve-01
                  :mod (h / hero))
            :time (a4 / after
                  :op1 (n4 / natural-disaster
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Katrina")))))

                                    :ARG2 (c / colleague))

                        :ARG0 y

# ::alignments
(c / captain-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Julie"
                  :op2 "Foudy"))
      :ARG1 (t / team
            :mod (s / soccer)
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "U.S."))
            :ARG0-of (w / win-01
                  :ARG1 (a / and
                        :op1 (g / game
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "World"
                                    :op2 "Cup"))
                        :op2 (m / medal
                              :mod (g2 / gold))
                        :subevent-of (g3 / game
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "The"
                                    :op2 "###"
                                    :op3 "Olympics"))))
            :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                  :ARG2 (t2 / team
                        :mod (s2 / sport)
                        :time (h / history
                              :poss (w2 / we))
                        :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (g4 / good-02
                                    :ARG1 t2)
                              :ARG3 (m2 / most))
                        :ARG1-of (h3 / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (l / love-01
                                    :ARG0 t2)
                              :ARG3 (m3 / most))))))
